sentences: Robert Kinelski (born Jan 17 1981 ) is an American mixing engineer, engineer, and record producer.

In 2020, Rob won four Grammy Awards, including Record of the Year, Album of the Year, Best Pop Vocal Album, and Best Engineered Album, Non-Classical for mixing Billie Eilish's debut album When We All Fall Asleep, Where Do We Go?.
